    <item>
      <guid isPermalink="false">528602</guid>
      <link>https://www.dnv.com/news/2026/03-statutory-imo-sub-committee-on-pollution-prevention-and-response-ppr13/</link>
      <title>IMO Sub-Committee on Pollution Prevention and Response (PPR13)</title>
      <description>The 13th session of the IMO’s Sub-Committee on Pollution Prevention and Response (PPR 13) was held in London from 9 to 13 February 2026. PPR commenced discussions on a legally binding framework on biofouling. PPR also agreed on amendments to requirements regarding NOx emissions certification for engines running on noncarbon fuels, P/V valves on new crude oil carriers, and the dewatering of oily bilge water.</description>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Feb 2026 01:52:00 GMT</pubDate>
      <media:content medium="image" url="https://www.dnv.com/contentassets/71a730adcdf8461ab91db72a04805a07/technical-regulatory-news-thumb---336x228-visible-area-286x194---200percent-2.png" />
    </item>
