      <title>DNV certifies ADNOC's West Aquifer CO₂ storage site at endorsement stage</title>
      <description>DNV today announced that ADNOC has been awarded a CO₂ Storage Certificate at the Site Endorsement stage for its West Aquifer CO₂ storage development, marking a significant milestone for the United Arab Emirates and the wider region in advancing large scale carbon capture and storage (CCS).</description>
