    <item>
      <guid isPermalink="false">528407</guid>
      <link>https://www.dnv.com/cyber/insights/news/norwegian-critical-infrastructure-organizations-cant-rest-on-their-laurels/</link>
      <title>Norwegian critical infrastructure organizations can’t rest on their laurels, warns DNV Cyber report</title>
      <description>What secured us yesterday won’t secure us tomorrow, advises DNV Cyber, as a new report shows that more than half (55%) of Norwegian executives working in critical infrastructure are confident in their organization’s ability to manage cyber threats.</description>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Feb 2026 07:46:00 GMT</pubDate>
      <media:content medium="image" url="https://www.dnv.com/siteassets/images/dnv-cyber/top-banner-article-event-pages-1440-x-554px/cyber-resilient-norway.jpg" />
    </item>
