      <link>https://www.dnv.com/cyber/insights/news/we-must-all-take-more-responsibility-to-protect-swedens-critical-infrastructure/</link>
      <title>“We must all take more responsibility to protect Sweden’s critical infrastructure”</title>
      <description>Swedish businesses and the public show strong support for greater government action to manage cyber-attacks, including tougher regulation and politically sensitive measures, but government cannot solve the problem alone.</description>
